@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Gateway
participant ChatService
participant MessageService
participant RabbitMQ
participant NotificationService

User -> Frontend: Send message
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /message
Gateway -> ChatService: validateChat()
ChatService -> MessageService: createMessage()
MessageService -> RabbitMQ: publish MessageCreated
RabbitMQ -> NotificationService: consume
NotificationService -> User: push notification
@enduml
